made shotgun terrariums all read 95% or greater.&amp;nbsp; I keep a cool mist humidifier running near the wood stove, and it's nice and cozy in here, even though there's nearly five feet of snow on the ground outside.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>9855188</next>\n<prev>9854753</prev>\n<first>9854396</first>\n<last>9856230</last>\n<when>1235493097</when>\n<utime>02/24/09 06:31 PM</utime>\n</post>"}